sellerCard.description: Hello! I'm Mujtaba, an experienced Engineer and Certified Web Developer with a proven track record spanning over 5 years in Web Design and Development.  I am  also a Cyber Security specialist with more than 3 years of experience in the field. Specializing in WordPress, I craft responsive and captivating websites that empower my clients to outshine their competitors. My expertise lies in creating dynamic and user-friendly WordPress websites that seamlessly adapt across all devices. Let's collaborate to bring your web vision to life and elevate your online presence.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What I need first before we start?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Provide domain & hosting services with cPanel.

Provide a logo, about us page, list of services, contact info, and reference websites.

Each service should have a 1-2 paragraph description.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you offer hosting or domain?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, we do not offer any. But we can develop your site on our temporary domains and at the end we will migrate your site to your hosting when its done.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will it be easy for me to edit my website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: We will provide a video walkthrough to teach you how to manage and do edits on your website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will my website be SEO friendly?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, on-page SEO will be included.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I'll show you a website that I like, can you create one similar to that?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Sure, I can create a wordpress website design similar to the one you like. Just show me the website and I will take it from there. I can also make changes to the design to fit your specific needs.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you redesign my existing website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes! I specialize in wordpress website designs and website redesigns, breathing new life into your existing site, enhancing its aesthetics, functionality, and user experience. Let's transform your online presence for better engagement and results.

reviews.comment:
Mujtaba went above and beyond in building my website, exceeding my expectations in every way. He was courteous, professional, and incredibly responsive throughout the process. Not only did he deliver a beautifully designed site, but he also provided a detailed walkthrough video, making it easy for me to update and manage my site moving forward.  

Before working with Mujtaba, I had hired another web designer who was overpriced and underdelivered. Mujtaba, on the other hand, did an impeccable job, and I continue to receive compliments on the look and feel of my site. I couldn’t be more pleased with the results. Highly recommend, 10/10!

seller_response.comment: It wasn't pleasure working with you. Thank you

reviews.comment: Mujtaba did an INCREDIBLE job on our new website, showing professionalism, meticulous attention to detail, and exceeding our expectations at every turn. His quick responsiveness and proactive communication made working with him an absolute joy, starting with a Zoom call just an hour after my request. I'm thrilled with the stunning, professional site he delivered and will definitely work with him again! 🙌

seller_response.comment: Thank you it was pleasure working with you.

reviews.comment: Stop searching! You’ve found the perfect freelancer for your website. They understood my needs with minimal direction, delivered high-quality work with a fast turnaround, and kept communication clear every step of the way. Kicking off the process with a video review set the tone for an outstanding experience. I highly recommend them for any web design project on Fiverr!

The developer did what he promised, which was to develop a functioning attractive website fully in line with the requirements. He communicated promptly and efficiently, followed up on requests, and made sure nothing was left hanging. By following up on requests until I was fully satisfied and by creating an instruction video on how to navigate the back end, he went beyond expectations. I highly recommend working with him.

Mujtaba was really pleasant to work with, and he was very patient and helpful throughout the process. He guided me through an issue we encountered with hosting my domain (which would've been very difficult for me to figure out on my own), and then he worked quite quickly once we were underway. I'm so pleased with the way that my website looks now!
